div.p:
PURSE To dream of loosing a purse, signifies good, if it be full;
but bad, if it be empty. To dream of finding a purse, is a very
favourable omen.

YOKE. To dream of having to bear the yoke, denotes danger,
if it be a woman, she will be ready and willing to obey her husband,
and careful to govern her family.
